<p>A source told People: 'Everyone’s happy and healthy, and they're extremely grateful. He's been an easy baby so far.'</p>

<p>The proud parents later gave a first glimpse at their new addition in a black-and-white photo of their hands holding his tiny feet.</p>

<p>She hinted at the baby's name in the photo's caption, writing: 'ForEver grateful for this true blessing.'</p>

